<plot>As a young businesswomen Claire appears self-reliant, intelligent and poised. She doesn't miss a beat, for every moment wasted breathes life into her fiercest opponent, tomorrow. Focused on her goals to stay ahead of the game, Claire unwittingly becomes the victim of a downward spiral. With her mortality at stake, Claire faces off with herself in a frightening battle for control of her life. Staring into the face of defeat, she sees herself. Time allows us to intimately experience the human struggle to realize our truths about success and happiness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?608343</url></doc>
